Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.26,Tema,,0,0,0,,¿Cuántos dólares son falsos?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.92,Tema,,0,0,0,,PUNTO: uno de cada dos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.02,Tema,,0,0,0,,Pero si hay amor, ¡Entonces hazlo!
