Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.85,Tema_Sheryl,,0,0,0,,...Aaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:27.99,Tema_Ranka,,0,0,0,,¿Qué hay de mi estrellaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:29.22,Tema_Sheryl,,0,0,0,,...Aaa uuu aaa...
